body_html: I commented on a CL internally regarding this. I'm not sure why that error message is being displayed in the docker environment. The "Can't find swig" error message was in our configure file and it was deleted by my SWIG change. Somehow that old code is lingering around, and failing, because we no longer apt-get swig in the Dockerfile.
